---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — BagHolderAI"
  description="Privacy Policy for BagHolderAI — what data we collect and how we use it."
  noAds
>

  {/* ============================================================ HERO */}
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pt-10 pb-6 sm:px-6 sm:pt-14 sm:pb-8">

    <h1 class="text-[28px] font-semibold leading-[1.12] tracking-tight
               text-text sm:text-[34px] md:text-[40px] md:leading-[1.08]">
      Privacy <span class="text-primary">policy</span>.
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-[14.5px] leading-[1.55] text-text-dim
              sm:text-[15px]">
      What data we collect, what we don't, and what happens with it.
      No cookies, no tracking, no surveillance.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 font-mono text-[10.5px]
                uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-text-muted">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-pos
                     shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(134,239,172,0.7)]"></span>
        last updated · April 2026
      </span>
      <span class="text-border">·</span>
      <span>cookieless analytics</span>
      <span class="text-border">·</span>
      <span>GDPR compliant</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ============================================================ MAIN */}
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pb-24 sm:px-6">

    {/* ============ § 1 — OVERVIEW ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-4 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 1 · Overview
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        BagHolderAI respects your privacy. This policy explains what
        data we collect and how we use it.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 2 — WHAT WE COLLECT ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 2 · What we collect
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim mb-4">
        <strong class="text-text font-semibold">Website analytics:</strong>{" "}
        We use Umami Cloud (a privacy-focused analytics tool) to collect
        anonymous usage statistics. Umami does not use cookies, does
        not track users across websites, and does not collect personal
        information. We see aggregate data only (page views, referrers,
        countries).
      </p>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim mb-4">
        <strong class="text-text font-semibold">Purchases:</strong>{" "}
        When you buy a product through Payhip (our payment processor),
        Payhip collects your payment information and email address. We
        receive your email and purchase details but never see or store
        your payment card information. Payhip acts as the merchant of
        record and handles all payment processing and EU VAT
        compliance.
      </p>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim mb-4">
        <strong class="text-text font-semibold">Email:</strong>{" "}
        If you contact us at bagholderai@proton.me, we receive your
        email address and message content.
      </p>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        <strong class="text-text font-semibold">Telegram:</strong>{" "}
        Our public Telegram channel (@BagHolderAI_report) broadcasts
        reports. We do not collect subscriber data beyond what Telegram
        provides to channel administrators (subscriber count, no
        individual identities).
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 3 — WHAT WE DON'T COLLECT ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 3 · What we don't collect
      </h2>

      <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          No cookies (Umami is cookieless)
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          No personal tracking
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          No advertising data
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          No third-party trackers
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          No credit card or payment details (handled entirely by Payhip)
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 4 — THIRD-PARTY SERVICES ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 4 · Third-party services
      </h2>

      <ul class="space-y-2 text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          <strong class="text-text font-semibold">Payhip</strong>{" "}
          (payments): subject to Payhip's privacy policy
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          <strong class="text-text font-semibold">Umami Cloud</strong>{" "}
          (analytics): privacy-focused, GDPR compliant, no personal
          data collected
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          <strong class="text-text font-semibold">Vercel</strong>{" "}
          (hosting): subject to Vercel's privacy policy
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          <strong class="text-text font-semibold">Supabase</strong>{" "}
          (database): stores trading data and project content only,
          no personal user data
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-4 before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-pos before:content-['›']">
          <strong class="text-text font-semibold">A-Ads</strong>{" "}
          (advertising): crypto-native ad network, may use its own
          tracking on ad units
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 5 — DATA RETENTION ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 5 · Data retention
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        We retain purchase records (email, product, date) for
        accounting purposes. We do not sell, share, or rent personal
        data to anyone.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 6 — YOUR RIGHTS ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 6 · Your rights
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        If you're in the EU, you have rights under GDPR including
        access, correction, and deletion of your data. Contact{" "}
        <a href="mailto:bagholderai@proton.me"
           class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover transition-colors
                  border-b border-primary/30 hover:border-primary">
          bagholderai@proton.me
        </a>{" "}
        for any data requests.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 7 — CHANGES ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 7 · Changes
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        We may update this policy as the project evolves. Changes will
        be posted on this page.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 8 — CONTACT ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 8 · Contact
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        <a href="mailto:bagholderai@proton.me"
           class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover transition-colors
                  border-b border-primary/30 hover:border-primary">
          bagholderai@proton.me
        </a>
      </p>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
